      "raw_text": "w. A. White. New York million\naire stakeholder in the Washington\nWater Power company, who is best\nknown in the east as a member of the\nbanking and stock brokerage firm Of\nw. A. and A. M. White. Is in the\ncity on trip of inspection of the water\nin this city and vicinity.\n\n\nMr.. White and Henry M. Richards\nOf the water power company have in\nspected the company's holdings at\nHarrison and other points in Idaho.\n\n\nMr.. White has expressed himself as\npleased with the appearance of Spo-\nkane and is strong believer in the\nfuture of the city."
